{"tid":425802,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［中二病］無人機與VR","createTime":"2017-10-06T04:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T14:07:35.000Z","uid":32331,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"421780d26acce65f60e8f3ffece3843778974089","tid":425802,"uid":32331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:54:21.000Z","msg":"其實現今科技已經可以結合無人機同VR技術，<br />\n<br />\n佢哋大多仲使用係航拍層面，點解唔將佢用係娛樂<br />\n<br />\n外國已經開始緊無人機飛行比賽嘅研究，機體設計，比賽場地等等，睇落真係幾吸引。<br />\n<br />\n再將四驅車，激鬥戰車等元素加入，結合3D打印，可以將佢哋嘅外殼，佢哋嘅部件，由自己嘅想像中逐一實現。<br />\n終於可以將動畫嘅內容實現<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c2af6f79c79e43608a3187222e909f81915e29","tid":425802,"uid":32331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"Oh, 被負評，乜唔好玩咩？"},{"pid":"540452fd2010918264cf2953b5e8fa048fdbd7c5","tid":425802,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:56:47.000Z","msg":"整d 可以遙控做出簡單動作既機械人,  再o係機械人放個cam ,<br />\n<br />\n玩家就睇住cam黎遙控 ,  咁就係簡單版 gundam build fighter"},{"pid":"d201dc18a739d414e7896a48c0fac94242764994","tid":425802,"uid":32331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整d 可以遙控做出簡單動作既機械人,  再o係機械人放個cam ,<br />\n<br />\n玩家就睇住cam黎遙控 ,  咁就係簡單版 gundam build fighter</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗應該睇下片先討論好啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1_XF5hYFbN4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1_XF5hYFbN4&d=Vw%2BPPaDukkvmVNujyjkxCEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=76b94278\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1_XF5hYFbN4</a>"},{"pid":"0152de87dee370e955792e60d57583c67e600632","tid":425802,"uid":88074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"已經有啦 <br />\n利申做緊"},{"pid":"99033911e40f6e428b675e52bb0f78868c4a36f1","tid":425802,"uid":32331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經有啦 <br />\n利申做緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾時會大搞，如果普及真係超正"},{"pid":"a32823189a3503b853c53296ddc95436d5badda2","tid":425802,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"成篇野1999<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅比賽咪fpv drone,一早有啦，研乜啦究<br />\n<br />\n3D print都唔係新野，但係你換part黎做乜？一架drone 嘅設計係要經過測試，俾你自己print舊野換上去好大機會會差過原本"},{"pid":"3f919a191ffa06dbe29012d7152eaf5f225314d2","tid":425802,"uid":32331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成篇野1999<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅比賽咪fpv drone,一早有啦，研乜啦究<br />\n<br />\n3D print都唔係新野，但係你換part黎做乜？一架drone 嘅設計係要經過測試，俾你自己print舊野換上去好大機會會差過原本</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我講嘅係一啲外形之類嘅部件，用3D打印自己整，<br />\n<br />\n我都話咗外國已經有啦，但香港未有啊，<br />\n<br />\n研究下點係香港興起囉，場地啊，玩法啊，香港都未有啦"}]}